- `ls_bare_file_in_cwd` ‚Äî `ls report` in cwd `projects` ‚Üí `projects/report`
- `ls_bare_segment_no_cwd` ‚Äî `ls report` with no cwd ‚Üí `/report` (root)
- Integration test: `ls` on a file path where path is single-segment in non-root cwd

The test coverage gap caused this to ship undetected. *Ferrum was not vigilant enough in the first pass ‚Äî noted.*

